# Django Project Rules

## Technology Stack
- Django web framework
- SQLite database
- HTML analysis and web scraping
- API interactions

## Structure
- `apps/` - Django applications
- `scripts/` - Utility scripts  
- `html_analysis_tools/` - HTML processing
- `tests/` - Test files

## Development Guidelines
- Follow Django best practices
- Write tests for new functionality
- Document complex logic
- Maintain separation of concerns
- Respect existing Django structure
- Don't move core Django files without permission
- Test Django functionality after changes
